{
  "stem": "935.9",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was just getting comfortable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Toward the end, when we were out of this block, we literally went from one night to the next.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had heard the rumors about Count Bernadotte.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Didn't quite know who or what, but as it turned our later on, that wonderful man had long, long before that tried to make a deal with Himmler to exchange against prisoners, German prisoners, you know, Swedish, and Danish and so on.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when the war went well for Germany, didn't want any part of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Toward the end, Himmler agreed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was agreed that they would come and take us, which was the last concentration camp being hid.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also, I must say that in the concentration camp, after the bunker, I accidentally met Gemma Gluck, a sweet old lady.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, she wasn't old then, I just thought she was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sweet sister of former mayor of New York, La Guardia, who was married to the Hungarian police president.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this is how she came, because I said, what does an American do in Ravensbruck or in a camp, look exactly like La Guardia.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Like chocolate pudding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Sweet woman.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I didn't know really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It didn't mean much to me, except I thought, I don't know where my mother is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Perhaps there's a young girl helping her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I helped her a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And Gemma Gluck also suddenly disappeared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In other words, they also needed her as a bargaining chip, of course, for some-- some big German who knows what.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They-- I don't know why only French, Belgian, and-- but I know that the clique of the goal was in that group.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
